Current Structure:
/										Root (PATH)
/data/									File databases, indexes and settings (PATH . DATA)
/includes/								Application (PeanutCMS) files (PATH . INC)
/includes/helpers/						Helper functions
/includes/models/						Data models
/includes/modules/						Modules (Controllers in MVC (kind of))
/includes/templates/					Dynamic interface content, e.g. html, css and js (Views in MVC)
/languages/								Languages (PATH . LANG)
/public/								Static interface content, e.g. css, js and images (PATH . PUBLIC)
/public/css/							Static stylesheets
/public/js/								Static javascripts
/themes/								Themes
/themes/arachis/						Arachis theme
/themes/arachis/templates/				Dynamic interface content

Proposed Structure:
/										Root (PATH)
/data/									File databases, indexes and settings (PATH . DATA)
/includes/								Application (PeanutCMS) files (PATH . INC)
/includes/helpers/						Helper functions
/includes/models/						Data models
/includes/modules/						Modules (Controllers in MVC (kind of))
/includes/templates/					Dynamic interface content, e.g. html, css and js (Views in MVC)
/languages/								Languages (PATH . LANG)
/plugins/								Plug-ins
/public/								Static interface content, e.g. css, js and images (PATH . PUBLIC)
/public/css/							Static stylesheets
/public/js/								Static javascripts
/public/images/
/themes/								Themes
/themes/arachis/						Arachis theme
/themes/arachis/templates/				Dynamic interface content